(989, '0', '2022-11-25 05:55:00', '<img src=\"http://thegarageblog.com/garage/wp-content/uploads/CTSext-500x305.jpg\" alt=\"Cadillac today unveiled the 2011 CTS Coupe, the latest and most\" />\nCadillac has released photos of what the production CTS Coupe will look like, and we are pleased to see it was faithful to the concept car. Sales are expected to start in Spring of 2010. Cadillac considers the CTS Coupe as the ‘centerpiece’ of the brand. Motivation of the CTS Coupe comes from a 3.6L [...]...<br><a href=\"http://thegarageblog.com/garage/preview-cadillac-cts-coupe/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: thegarageblog.com</a><br>', 'Preview: Cadillac CTS Coupe'),
