(1055, '2', '2022-11-25 18:17:27', 'At the Society of Motor Manufacturers and Traders (SMMT) conference, Lord Mandelson has pledged to put up cash to secure Vauxhall’s future in the UK if ongoing talks eventually reveal General Motors Co.’s commitment to the country.\nLord Mandelson spoke to Autocar and said that taxpayers’ money would be brought out depending on what GM Europe [...]...<br><a href=\"http://www.4wheelsnews.com/britain-to-support-gm-for-vauxhalls-future/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: www.4wheelsnews.com</a><br>', 'Britain to support GM for Vauxhall’s future'),
