(1057, '2', '2022-11-25 17:54:55', 'General Motors announced today that the brand new 2010 Opel Astra was awarded with five stars for safety, the top rating for new tough regulations that took effect this year. The new vehicle received the highest points ever awarded for Astra’s active head restraints which protect against whiplash but it also scored very well on [...]...<br><a href=\"http://www.4wheelsnews.com/2010-opel-astra-receives-five-star-euro-ncap-safety-rating/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: www.4wheelsnews.com</a><br>', '2010 Opel Astra receives five-star Euro NCAP safety rating'),
(1058, '2', '2022-11-25 18:09:56', '<img src=\"http://blog.caranddriver.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/Gullwing-America-SLS-Panamerica-440x268.jpg\" alt=\"Gullwing-America-SLS-Panamerica\" />\nBy now regular readers know that the brand-new Mercedes-Benz SLS AMG is styled to recall the Mercedes 300SL Gullwing from the 1950s. But if the supercar’s looks aren’t retro enough for your tastes, allow us to introduce you to Gullwing America.\nThe Texas-based company now offers an aluminum-and-carbon-fiber body kit to make the SLS look even [...]\n\n\nNo related posts....<br><a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/caranddriver/blog/~3/W5e8SZdroOE/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feedproxy.google.com</a><br>', 'SLS AMG Not Gullwing-y Enough? Gullwing America Has the Fix'),
(1059, '2', '2022-11-25 17:55:57', '<img src=\"http://blog.caranddriver.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/2011-Infiniti-M56-placement-440x268.jpg\" alt=\"2011 Infiniti M56\" />\nSticking with the athletic cut.\nInfiniti has styled itself as the Japanese BMW, but for most of the two decades the brand has been around, its products haven’t measured up to those from the German company. Recently, though, we’ve watched the G sedan and coupe evolve into some mighty formidable competition for the 3-series, while the [...]\n\n\nNo related posts....<br><a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/caranddriver/blog/~3/uvZBSDeWmSo/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feedproxy.google.com</a><br>', '2011 Infiniti M37 / M56 – Preview'),
(1060, '2', '2022-11-25 17:54:37', '<img src=\"http://blog.caranddriver.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/2010-Mitsubishi-Lancer-Evolution-MR-Touring-placement-440x268.jpg\" alt=\"2010 Mitsubishi Lancer Evolution MR Touring\" />\nA slightly more evolved Evo.\nWhat Is It?\n\nA slightly more comfortable version of the iconic Mitsubishi Lancer Evolution. As its name suggests, it’s based on the Evo MR, with its six-speed dual-clutch automated manual gearbox. The Evo MR Touring presents a somewhat subtler visual image with its less obnoxious rear wing while making occupants a bit [...]\n\n\nNo related posts....<br><a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/caranddriver/blog/~3/w1FUOGIJBGY/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feedproxy.google.com</a><br>', '2010 Mitsubishi Lancer Evolution MR Touring – Quick Spin'),
