(1062, '2', '2022-11-25 12:11:00', '\r\n  \r\nPosted on 11.25.2009 12:11 \r\n    by\r\n    Maxx Biker\r\nFiled under:\r\n    Ducati  |  parts accesories  |  apparel  | Motorcycles  | Motorcycle News Say you have a Ducatisti in the house and don’t really know what to buy him/her for Christmas. Things are now made much easier for you with this new website that Pro Italia and Ducati have launched – Ducatigifts.com. Offering performance parts and accessories, protective gear and casual Ducati clothing, the site is like Santa’s bag of goodies for each and every fan of the Italian brand.Press release is attached after the jump. Pro Italia &...<br><a href=\"http://www.topspeed.com/motorcycles/motorcycle-news/pro-italia-ducati-team-up-to-launch-ducatigiftscom-ar82091.html\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: www.topspeed.com</a><br>', 'Pro Italia & Ducati team up to launch Ducatigifts.com'),
