(1110, '2', '2022-11-25 23:36:53', '<img src=\"http://www.egmcartech.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/cadillac_cts_coupe_concept_main1.jpg\" alt=\"cadillac_cts_coupe_concept_main\" />\nOctober saw the first monthly sales gain in almost two years for GM, according to Detroit News.  The Detroit automaker has slashed costs by almost $30 billion and has brought itself to a pot where it expects to start repaying federal loans next month.\nThese are all great signs, but in order to post a [...]...<br><a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/egmcartech/~3/3l_mNQyF3rQ/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feedproxy.google.com</a><br>', 'GM’s turnaround fueled by hot products'),
