(1447, '2', '2022-11-30 19:20:57', '<img src=\"http://www.egmcartech.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/lamborghini_gallardo_lp560_4_polizia_crash.jpg\" alt=\"Lamborghini Gallardo LP560-4 Polizia Crash\" />\nAfter spending an year with the Italian State Police, the new Lamborghini Gallardo LP560-4 Polizia ended up being totaled in an accident near Cremona this past weekend. The story goes that the driver of the Gallardo LP560-4 Polizia swerved to avoid a car that was exiting a gas station and ended up driving into a [...]...<br><a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/egmcartech/~3/B4oBAtsGxb8/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feedproxy.google.com</a><br>', 'Italy’s Lamborghini Gallardo LP560-4 Polizia totalled in accident'),
