(1587, '2', '2022-12-01 18:46:17', 'Infiniti announced today that a special limited edition of the FX 37/ FX 50 called Millionaire. This new edition which will be produced in just 100 units, will be revealed on December 14 at the Amsterdam RAI.\nPriced at €95.450, the new Infiniti FX 37/ FX 50 Millionaire Edition will feature a dark graphite finish, roof rails, [...]...<br><a href=\"http://www.4wheelsnews.com/2010-infiniti-fx-millionaire-edition-to-debut-at-2009-amsterdam-rai/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: www.4wheelsnews.com</a><br>', '2010 Infiniti FX Millionaire Edition to debut at 2009 Amsterdam RAI'),
(1588, '2', '2022-12-01 19:07:07', '<img src=\"http://blog.caranddriver.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/Buick-GMC-logo-1-220x134.jpg\" alt=\"Buick-GMC-logo-1\" />\nMichael Richards, previously general marketing manager of Lincoln-Mercury (and not Kramer on Seinfeld), has been named head of Buick and GMC. Richards replaces Susan Docherty, who has been promoted to head all sales at GM, replacing Mark LaNeve, who left GM in October.\n\n\nNo related posts.\n\n\nNo related posts....<br><a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/caranddriver/blog/~3/L5pXY2bnyqU/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feedproxy.google.com</a><br>', 'General Motors Names New Head of Buick and GMC'),
(1589, '2', '2022-12-01 19:12:24', '<img src=\"http://www.egmcartech.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/2006_ford_explorer.jpg\" alt=\"2006_ford_explorer\" />\nThe Supreme Court has decided to turn down FoMoCo’s appeal of a California decision that granted $82.6 million in damages to Benetta Buell-Wilson, who was involved in an accident that left here paralyzed from the waist down, due mainly to poor production and a risky design that Ford supposedly was aware of.\nFord was not contending [...]...<br><a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/egmcartech/~3/vEKdCe8K8OM/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feedproxy.google.com</a><br>', 'Supreme Court grants no relief for Ford in SUV rollover case'),
