(2218, '3', '2022-12-06 15:51:14', '<img src=\"http://thegarageblog.com/garage/wp-content/uploads/abarth-paddock-1000-500x375.jpg\" alt=\"abarth paddock 1000\" />\nOne of the great things about Italians is their passion for the good things in life. Fortunately that passion extends to cars and motorsport, especially Italian cars. The good folks at Abarth have been sticking scorpion badges on Fiats for many years, most recently Fiat’s new 500 and they wanted to share their passion for [...]...<br><a href=\"http://thegarageblog.com/garage/abarth-shows-off-at-mugello/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: thegarageblog.com</a><br>', 'Abarth shows off at Mugello'),
(2219, '3', '2022-12-06 18:25:28', '<img src=\"http://thegarageblog.com/garage/wp-content/uploads/biggsb-racing-burnt-500x375.jpg\" alt=\"biggsb racing burnt\" />\nAs I mentioned, the BIGGSB Racing Subaru have had some challenges at the 25 Hours of Thunderhill. Twitter user @kplaird has shared a bunch of photos of the rather forlorn looking WRX sporting numerous wounds. The fuel cell is bent, and the hood is sporting some creative new coloring thanks to a leaky turbo oil [...]...<br><a href=\"http://thegarageblog.com/garage/biggsb-racing-subaru-having-some-challenges/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: thegarageblog.com</a><br>', 'BIGGSB Racing Subaru having some challenges'),
