(2241, '3', '2022-12-07 04:00:18', '<img src=\"http://images.thecarconnection.com/lrg/new-york-yankees-2010-ford-mustang-gt_100276854_l.jpg\" alt=\"http://images.thecarconnection.com/lrg/new-york-yankees-2010-ford-mustang-gt_100276854_l.jpg\" />A one-of-a-kind 2010 Ford Mustang GT known as the \"New York Yankees Mustang,\" is up for auction. The car has been created to celebrate the opening of a new stadium for the famous baseball team and it even features the signature of Derek Jeter on its dashboard.According to Doyle, the signature Yankees pinstripe paint job and logo was applied before the Yankees won the 2009 World Series. \"The World Series win for the Yankees this year only adds to the provenance of this unique collector car. Plus, the dashboard is signed by the 2009 SI Sportsman of the Year, Derek Jeter\" he said.The one-off car ...<br><a href=\"http://benzs.blogspot.com/2009/12/auction-2010-new-york-yankees-mustang.html\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: benzs.blogspot.com</a><br>', 'Auction: 2010 New York Yankees Mustang GT'),
