(2306, '3', '2022-12-08 14:59:44', '\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nLeading both Chrysler and Fiat has to be a lot of responsibility, so it comes as little surprise that the CEO of both automakers, Sergio Marchionne, plans to abdicate one of the two positions within the next 24 months. Marchionne did strongly hint which company would soldier on without his leadership.\n\n“This cannot go on forever,” [...]\n\n\n...<br><a href=\"http://feeds.leftlanenews.com/click.phdo?i=f029efcc2ccda8f9b9d98bff2518777c\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feeds.leftlanenews.com</a><br>', 'Marchionne to depart Fiat or Chrysler within 24 months'),
