(2325, '3', '2022-12-09 19:10:24', '<img src=\"http://www.wired.com/images_blogs/autopia/2009/12/schwarzenegger_with_audi_01.jpg\" alt=\"schwarzenegger_with_audi_01\" />\nFor all the attention Audi’s silent and sexy electric e-tron concept is getting, building the two-seat, four-motor EV apparently has been emasculating. What else could explain all the tough-guy posturing we’ve seen lately?\nThough the e-tron stole the limelight at the Frankfurt auto show and was even sexier in person at the Los Angeles Auto Show, [...]...<br><a href=\"http://feeds.wired.com/~r/wiredautopia/~3/yU86_1BZRkQ/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feeds.wired.com</a><br>', 'Autopia WTF? Governator-Edition Caption Contest'),
