(2372, '3', '2022-12-07 17:00:00', '<img src=\"http://img.worldcarfans.com/2009/12/23421.tn.jpg\" alt=\"http://img.worldcarfans.com/2009/12/23421.tn.jpg\" /> Two new Renaulsport Twingo models for wannabe rally drivers have been released.  Are they cost effective for all drivers?  Details inside.\r\n \r\n...<br><a href=\"http://feeds.worldcarfans.com/~r/worldcarfans/Jxfz/~3/o57D_8aHrEs/renault-twingo-rs-entry-level-rally-cars-announced\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feeds.worldcarfans.com</a><br>', ' Renault Twingo RS Entry-Level Rally Cars Announced'),
