(2376, '3', '2022-12-10 10:07:14', '<img src=\"http://www.automobilesreview.com/uploads/2009/12/bentley-continental-supersports-thumb.jpg\" alt=\"Bentley Continental Supersports sets new eco-standarts\" />The latest Bentley Continental Supersports, which is also the first Bentley fitted with FlexFuel technology which allows it to run on E85 biofuel, gasoline or any combination of these two fuels, has further demonstrate its eco-friendliness by meeting the 85% recyclability standard.\nThis certification is given only to vehicles which parts can be reused or reprocessed [...]...<br><a href=\"http://www.automobilesreview.com/auto-news/bentley-continental-supersports-flexfuel/20011/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: www.automobilesreview.com</a><br>', 'Bentley Continental Supersports sets new eco-standarts'),
(2377, '3', '2022-12-10 08:37:01', '<img src=\"http://www.automobilesreview.com/uploads/2009/12/Nissan-370Z-40th-Anniversary-Edition-thumb.jpg\" alt=\"Nissan announced the 370Z 40th Anniversary Edition’s price\" />Limited to only 1,000 units and released specially to celebrate the 40th anniversary of the original Datsun 240Z, the Nissan 370Z 40th Anniversary Edition is now priced at $38,860 USD. The limited production Z Coupe is scheduled to go on sale in early spring 2010.\nThe 40th Anniversary Edition starts with the 370Z Touring model fitted [...]...<br><a href=\"http://www.automobilesreview.com/auto-news/nissan-370z-40th-anniversary-edition-price/20009/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: www.automobilesreview.com</a><br>', 'Nissan announced the 370Z 40th Anniversary Edition’s price'),
(2378, '3', '2022-12-09 16:45:10', '<img src=\"http://www.automobilesreview.com/uploads/2009/12/Vorsteiner-Carrera-VGT-thumb.jpg\" alt=\"Vorsteiner releases V-GT aero kit for 2010 Porsche Carrera\" />Vorsteiner has released a supreme aerodynamic kit for the 2010 Porsche Carrera MKII facelift, which is named V-GT. Combining both elegance and simplicity, the new aero pack from Vorsteiner upgrades even further the factory vision of the sports ride without any compromises in quality and performance. The V-GT kit from Vorsteiner will fit the Porsche: [...]...<br><a href=\"http://www.automobilesreview.com/auto-news/vorsteiner-v-gt-2010-porsche-carrera/20007/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: www.automobilesreview.com</a><br>', 'Vorsteiner releases V-GT aero kit for 2010 Porsche Carrera'),
(2379, '3', '2022-12-09 15:32:35', '<img src=\"http://www.automobilesreview.com/uploads/2009/12/GeigerCars-Cadillac-CTS-V-thumb.jpg\" alt=\"Cadillac CTS-V by GeigerCars\" />After GeigerCars special performance programme, the European market newcomer Cadillac CTS-V is ready to face Germany’s finest performance saloons – Audi RS6, BMW M5 and the new Mercedes-Benz E63 AMG. Instead of Cadillac CTS-V’s stock engine output data of 564 horsepower and 747 Nm of maximum torque, the GeigerCars version is capable to produce the [...]...<br><a href=\"http://www.automobilesreview.com/auto-news/geigercars-cadillac-cts-v/20004/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: www.automobilesreview.com</a><br>', 'Cadillac CTS-V by GeigerCars'),
(2380, '3', '2022-12-09 17:00:59', '<img src=\"http://www.autofans.us/images/Nissan/2010%20Nissan%20Qashqai%201.jpg\" alt=\"2010 Nissan Qashqai\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n The Nissan Qashqai has a silly name. Though not as silly as the Qashqai+2, the seven-seat version of the British built small CUV. But silly name not withstanding, the slightly smaller than a Nissan Rogue compact crossover has been something of a sales phenom for Nissan, selling more than 500,000 copies around the world [...]...<br><a href=\"http://www.autofans.us/2009/12/09/nissan-updates-qashqai-crossover-and-no-were-still-not-gonna-get-it/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: www.autofans.us</a><br>', 'Nissan updates Qashqai crossover - and no, we’re still not gonna get it'),
(2381, '3', '2022-12-09 16:19:06', '<img src=\"http://www.autofans.us/images/Mercedes-Benz/2010%20Mercedes%20ML450%20Hybrid%201.jpg\" alt=\"2010 Mercedes ML450 Hybrid\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n The 2010 Mercedes ML450 Hybrid is the first full hybrid vehicle from Mercedes and, to better understand the experience of owning one, I sat in horrendous Los Angeles traffic for an hour.\nHaving driven the ML320 in diesel trim, I’ve never been convinced of the need for something like a hyrbid in the lineup. But [...]...<br><a href=\"http://www.autofans.us/2009/12/09/quick-drive2010-mercedes-ml450-hybrid/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: www.autofans.us</a><br>', 'Quick Drive:2010 Mercedes ML450 Hybrid'),
(2382, '3', '2022-12-09 15:36:37', '<img src=\"http://www.autofans.us/images/Audi/2009%20Audi%20R8%205%202%20FSI%20Quattro%201.jpg\" alt=\"2009 Audi R8 5 2 FSI Quattro\" />How much is half a second and 105 horsepower worth to you? You’ll want to ponder that question if you’re in the enviable position of having to decide between the V-8-propelled version of Audi’s R8 two-seat, mid-engine exotic or the newly introduced V-10 edition. When the cars are similarly configured, the ten’s two additional cylinders [...]...<br><a href=\"http://www.autofans.us/2009/12/09/first-test-2009-audi-r8-52-fsi-quattro/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: www.autofans.us</a><br>', 'First Test: 2009 Audi R8 5.2 FSI Quattro'),
(2383, '3', '2022-12-09 15:12:59', '<img src=\"http://www.autofans.us/images/Suzuki/2010%20Suzuki%20Kizashi%20GTS%201.jpg\" alt=\"2010 Suzuki Kizashi GTS\" />The 2010 Suzuki Kizashi will change the way you look at Suzuki. To put it bluntly, the Kizashi is the strongest evidence yet that Suzuki’s automotive division is no longer operating on autopilot in the States. And what’s more, the brand is showing serious confidence. Consider the vehicles against which the automaker wants you to [...]...<br><a href=\"http://www.autofans.us/2009/12/09/review-2010-suzuki-kizashi-gts-is-up-for-the-challenge/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: www.autofans.us</a><br>', 'Review: 2010 Suzuki Kizashi GTS is up for the Challenge'),
(2384, '3', '2022-12-09 14:50:02', '<img src=\"http://www.autofans.us/images/Chevrolet/2012%20Chevrolet%20Spark%201.jpg\" alt=\"2012 Chevrolet Spark\" />Chevrolet likes to pretend that the Chevrolet Spark is the car you chose. The first hint of its design came as a two-door concept version called Beat, at the 2007 New York auto show. The Beat appeared as part of a trio of concepts, alongside a micro-crossover called Trax and a retro minivan, Groove.\nThe public [...]...<br><a href=\"http://www.autofans.us/2009/12/09/drive-experience-2012-chevrolet-spark-european-spec/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: www.autofans.us</a><br>', 'Drive Experience: 2012 Chevrolet Spark European Spec');
