(2401, '3', '2022-12-09 20:34:30', 'Pricing for the 2010 Hyundai Tucson, which goes on sale this month, has just been released. The base model with the manual transmission starts from $19,790 while the six-speed automatic retails for $20,790. Both prices include $795 for shipping. \n The Tucson has new features that include a 2.4-liter four-cylinder engine, which generates 176 hp [...]...<br><a href=\"http://www.4wheelsnews.com/2010-hyundai-tucson-us-pricing-announced/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: www.4wheelsnews.com</a><br>', '2010 Hyundai Tucson U.S. pricing announced'),
