(2529, '3', '2022-12-08 23:58:33', '<img src=\"http://fancytuning.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/gemballa-porsche-cayenne-gt500-aero-3.jpg\" alt=\"gemballa-porsche-cayenne-gt500-aero-3\" />\nA few days ago Gemballa released a new tuning kit for the Porsche Cayenne called the GT500 Aero 3 package. The German tuners created the Aero 3 kit consisting of several new body pieces to give it an aggressive look with added aerodynamics. Included in the package is a redesigned front bumper, side skirts, and [...]...<br><a href=\"http://fancytuning.com/2009/12/gemballa-porsche-cayenne-gt500-aero-3/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: fancytuning.com</a><br>', 'Gemballa Porsche Cayenne GT500 Aero 3'),
