(2567, '3', '2022-12-10 16:44:32', '<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_FmJ3CipQNPw/SyEW-xWMo6I/AAAAAAAAEp0/2nk77ia0U9g/s320/car_photo_347401_7.jpg\" alt=\"\" />The Qazana is inching closer to showrooms, as these spy shots prove. Nissan’s compact SUV stunner stole the limelight at March’s Geneva Motor Show – and this prototype reveals the distinctive looks will be carried over to the final version. Dominating the aggressive nose will be a mouth-shaped grille and large headlights. There’s also a low, rakish roofline and short overhangs front and rear. Inside, reports suggest the Qazana will take cues from the concept’s striking cabin. That means we can expect a protruding dash and a centre console inspired by a motorcycle fuel tank. The car w...<br><a href=\"http://dikarockz.blogspot.com/2009/12/spied-2011-nissan-qazana.html\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: dikarockz.blogspot.com</a><br>', 'Spied: 2011 Nissan Qazana'),
