(2618, '3', '2022-12-10 22:50:54', '<img src=\"http://www.wired.com/images_blogs/autopia/2009/12/usedcars.jpg\" alt=\"usedcars\" />\nSay you’re not richer than Croesus or even Bill Gates. Say you’re like us here at Autopia, and you don’t have money to burn and you’re looking to buy a car. You want to minimize the amount of cash you’re paying, and you’re looking for all the ways you can do that.\nDid you know that [...]...<br><a href=\"http://feeds.wired.com/~r/wiredautopia/~3/CKyp4KQjJTo/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feeds.wired.com</a><br>', 'The Ten Best Days of the Year to Buy a Car'),
