(2752, '3', '2022-12-12 01:34:53', '<img src=\"http://www.egmcartech.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/mercedes_bmw_main.jpg\" alt=\"Mercedes-Benz / BMW\" />\nBMW and Mini have entered into an agreement with Mercedes-Benz USA by which the latter will be responsible for the former two companies’ vehicles being imported through the port of Baltimore.\nBMW and Mini will use the Mercedes-Benz vehicle preparation center to inspect, process, and repair their pre-delivered vehicles starting in March.  President of BMW [...]...<br><a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/egmcartech/~3/OTYVF-5_Wqs/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feedproxy.google.com</a><br>', 'Mercedes-Benz and BMW team up for vehicle preparation'),
