(2914, '3', '2022-12-14 20:57:00', '<img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/green.autoblog.com/media/2009/12/chevy-volt-dance.jpg\" alt=\"\" />Filed under: LA Auto Show, Hybrid, Marketing/Advertising, Videos, Chevrolet, GM, Humor, Electric\r\nChevrolet Volt Dance - Click above to watch the video after the break\r\n\r\n\"E for electricity, V for Chevy Volt and me...\" Catchy little diddly, sure. But we were mostly willing to let the Chevrolet Volt song make the deep, dark trek into obscurity with nary another mention. That is, until today. What made us change our tune, you ask? Boy, are you in for a treat.\r\n\r\nWitness the Chevy Volt dance. Yes, it is an official routine apparently commissioned by GM. Showgoers that meandered near the GM area a...<br><a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/weblogsinc/autoblog/~3/_Zug0nC7csU/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feedproxy.google.com</a><br>', 'VIDEO: GM commissions Chevrolet Volt dance to go with song. Yes, really.'),
