(3002, '0', '2022-12-15 14:00:44', '<img src=\"http://www.egmcartech.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/2011_kia_forte_koup_main_a.jpg\" alt=\"2011 Kia Forte Koup\" />\nThe 2010 Kia Forte Koup is currently offered in two different trim-levels including the EX and SX. The Forte Koup EX is powered by a 156-hp 2.0L 4-cylinder, while the SX is powered by a 173-hp 2.4L 4-cylinder. Now what if you added a turbocharger to either or – you’d have a really fun Korean Koup or [...]...<br><a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/egmcartech/~3/jc8G81KfQ5k/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feedproxy.google.com</a><br>', '2012 Kia Forte Koup to get turbocharged 4-cylinder'),
