(3055, '0', '2022-12-15 17:55:51', '<img src=\"http://www.egmcartech.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/review_2010_volkswagen_gti_images_main.jpg\" alt=\"Review: 2010 Volkswagen GTI\" />\nSimply amazing.  Those are the two words we would pick to best describe the 2010 Volkswagen GTI; it deserves nothing less.  The Mark 6, though only a slight progression over the Mark 5, leaves little to be desired in a compact car; it is stonkingly fast, fuel-efficient, practical, and affordable.\nRead on as we [...]...<br><a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/egmcartech/~3/0W4vqadhMrg/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feedproxy.google.com</a><br>', 'Review: 2010 Volkswagen GTI unleashes the demon inside you'),
