(3078, '0', '2022-12-15 21:19:13', '<img src=\"http://blog.caranddriver.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/Audi-E-Tron-Concept-21-440x268.jpg\" alt=\"Audi-E-Tron-Concept-21\" />\nAudi tries to win us over with this electric supercar.\nToday’s hype machine tells us that electric power is to the internal-combustion engine what jets were to the propeller-driven airplane. Jet engines, of course, provided very clear advantages over the propeller engines they replaced—foremost, they offered higher speed.\n\nBut does an electric motor make a car run [...]\n\n\nRelated posts:Audi E-Tron Concept – Official Photos and InfoAudi E-Tron Concept Leaks onto InternetAudi Launches Viral Mini-Site for Electric “E-Tron” Concept, Possible Electrified R8...<br><a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/caranddriver/blog/~3/ocTpsN-D20s/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feedproxy.google.com</a><br>', 'Audi E-Tron Concept – Prototype Drive'),
(3079, '0', '2022-12-15 20:47:04', '<img src=\"http://blog.caranddriver.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/Bugatti-Veyron-Nocturne-12-440x268.jpg\" alt=\"Bugatti-Veyron-Nocturne-12\" />\nThis year marks a century of existence for automaker Bugatti, and among the company’s celebrations include this trio of limited-edition Veyrons. The three cars celebrate the company’s sales success in Middle Eastern markets and were unveiled today at the Dubai Motor Show. Just five copies of each car will be built, and they’re exclusively for [...]\n\n\nRelated posts:2009 Bugatti Veyron 16.4 Grand Sport – VideoGalibier? Veyron Lite? We Bug Bugatti About its Next Model2009 Bugatti Veyron 16.4 Grand Sport – First Drive Review...<br><a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/caranddriver/blog/~3/JdPhjD4DrS0/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feedproxy.google.com</a><br>', 'Bugatti Builds Three Special-Edition Veyrons for the Middle East'),
