(3081, '0', '2022-12-15 20:51:04', '<img src=\"http://www.egmcartech.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/lamborghini_ankonian_study_images_main.jpg\" alt=\"Lamborghini Ankonian (by Slavche Tanevski)\" />\nMeet the new Lamborghini Ankonian, a design study by Slavche Tanevski, a student at the Munich University of Applied Sciences. His project was completed in the fourth semester under the theme Lamborghini Raw Materials, which was led by Professor Dr. Othmar Wickenheiser.\nKeeping with the tradition of Lamborghini’s naming theme, Tanevski calls his study “Ankonian,” a [...]...<br><a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/egmcartech/~3/BqmePjLVMdk/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feedproxy.google.com</a><br>', 'Lamborghini Ankonian by Tanevski: Batmobile meets the Reventon'),
