(3125, '0', '2022-12-16 00:41:46', '<img src=\"http://blog.caranddriver.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/Audi-A7-Sportback-concept-placement-440x268.jpg\" alt=\"Audi A7 Sportback concept\" />\nAudi gives the four-door-fastback-coupe-thingie segment a touch of beauty.\nThe quest to fill market niches is not over yet: some carmakers are creating new vehicle categories and others are reintroducing classic shapes from the past. Returning from the old times is the four-door fastback, which enjoyed a rather brief period of popularity—mainly in the 1970s. In [...]\n\n\nRelated posts:Audi A7 Sportback Concept – Auto ShowsAudi E-Tron Concept – Prototype DriveAudi A1 Sportback Concept – Auto Shows...<br><a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/caranddriver/blog/~3/3w5NahnLIko/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feedproxy.google.com</a><br>', 'Audi A7 Sportback Concept – Prototype Drive'),
