(3127, '0', '2022-12-16 00:48:49', '<img src=\"http://www.egmcartech.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/2010_honda_insight_hybrid_wtd_a_images_002.jpg\" alt=\"2010 Honda Insight (Weekly Test-Drive)\" />\nAfter saying farewell to the 2010 Lincoln MKT EcoBoost, we welcomed the 2010 Honda Insight to our garage this week. The 5-passenger 2010 Honda Insight is powered by a 1.3L 4-cylinder i-VTEC gasoline engine and a 10kw electric-motor. The system helps the Insight hybrid achieve an EPA rated fuel-economy of 40/43 mpg (city/highway) and a [...]...<br><a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/egmcartech/~3/2hLO_9WAoiI/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feedproxy.google.com</a><br>', 'Weekly Test-Drive: 2010 Honda Insight gives us mixed feelings'),
