(3265, '0', '2022-12-16 22:19:36', '<img src=\"http://www.egmcartech.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/volkswagen_passat_cc_r_line_press_images_main.jpg\" alt=\"2010 Volkswagen Passat CC R-Line\" />\nVolkswagen announced today that it is extending its R-Line equipment package to the Passat CC, giving the model a more sportier and aggressive stance.\nOn the outside, the Passat CC R-Line features 17-inch (optional 18-inch) R-Line “Mallory” alloy wheels wrapped in 235/45 tires. The front spoiler and side skirts, each painted in body color, also add [...]...<br><a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/egmcartech/~3/q2qq7wRZc6o/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feedproxy.google.com</a><br>', '2010 Volkswagen Passat CC R-Line gives Passat CC a sportier look'),
(3266, '0', '2022-12-16 21:43:40', '<img src=\"http://www.egmcartech.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/2011_bmw_740i_main_a.jpg\" alt=\"2011 BMW 740i\" />\nThe previous generation of the BMW 7-Series only offered two engine choices including a V8 or a V12. Come Spring 2010, BMW will offer its twin-turbocharged inline 6-cylinder engine in the 2011 BMW 740i and the 2011 BMW 740Li. Both models will make their debut at the 2010 Detroit Auto Show next month.\nThe two models [...]...<br><a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/egmcartech/~3/6roaOtclvqA/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feedproxy.google.com</a><br>', '2010 Detroit Preview: 2011 BMW 740i, 740Li to get twin-turbo inline-6'),
