(3430, '0', '2022-12-17 22:31:56', '<img src=\"http://www.egmcartech.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/chevrolet_suburban_wide_main_a.jpg\" alt=\"Chevrolet Suburban \" />\nRemember the “Like a Rock” slogan for Chevrolet’s pickups and SUVs? Well, you’ll start hearing it less and less as GM’s most important brand shifts to concentrate more on passenger cars and crossovers. According to Chevrolet’s general manager Jim Campbell, 61 percent of the brand’s volume sales are outside the United States.\nNonetheless, he said that “Chevrolet’s [...]...<br><a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/egmcartech/~3/91-sVnZPNFA/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feedproxy.google.com</a><br>', 'Chevrolet to focus less on full-size pickups and SUVs'),
